# Always restart app and open browser (do it yourself every time)

**Rule:** After any code change that affects the damin-gambit web app, always:

1. **Restart the web server**  
   Stop any running uvicorn (e.g. `pkill -f "uvicorn damin_gambit.webapp"` or kill process on port 8000), then start it again:
   ```bash
   cd /Users/vukadin/GolandProjects/daminGambit
   PYTHONPATH=src .venv/bin/python -m uvicorn damin_gambit.webapp:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000
   ```

2. **Open the app in Cursor**  
   Open http://127.0.0.1:8000 **inside Cursor**: **Cmd+Shift+P** (Mac) or **Ctrl+Shift+P** (Windows/Linux) → run **"Simple Browser: Show"** → enter `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.  
   Alternatively run `open http://127.0.0.1:8000` to open in the system browser.

Do this every time after such code changes, without the user having to ask, so they can run queries (e.g. “za danas”, “tiket od 10 parova”) without manually restarting.
